## View the result​
To view the result when **creating a new request** :
1. **Open the Requests section**.
2. **Create a request**.
**As a result** , Creatio will display the number of the last created request, increased by 1, and the city of the current user on the page of a new request. The values will be retrieved from the corresponding system settings. [View the result >>>](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?ver=8.0&id=15362&anchor=view-result)
To view the result when **copying an existing request** :
1. **Create a request** that has an arbitrary name. For example, "Request’s name."
2. **Copy an existing request**. For example, "Request’s name." To do this, click ![](https://academy.creatio.com/docs/sites/academy_en/files/documentation/sdk/en/BPMonlineWebSDK/Screenshots/ManageTheSystemSettingValues/8.0/scr_Properties_button.png) → **Copy**.
3. **Set an arbitrary request name**. For example, "Sick leave."
**As a result** , Creatio will display the number of the last created request, increased by 1, and the city of the current user on the page of a copied request. The values will be retrieved from the corresponding system settings. [View the result >>>](https://academy.creatio.com/documents?ver=8.0&id=15362&anchor=view-result-1)
